- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses graph partition algorithms to solve the word segmentation problem. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with text processing and segmentation, which is relevant to information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper uses graph theory to model the sentence as a graph.
